long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tune Tailor for YouTube® : It's the same YouTube®  you love but Tailored just for you.

Easily adjust the playback rate for a video by clicking the `+` and `-` on the control bar.

Features:
- Seamless integration with YouTube's UI
- Allow for speeds over 2x
- Fast-forward through Ads
- Scope speed settings per video category (e.g. Ads, Music, Howto & Style, etc.)
- Works on embedded YouTube®  videos (iframes)
